<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>jQuery .slideToggle() </title>
   	<style>
     .wrap {
        height: 50px;
        background-color: #dcdcdc;
        border: 3px solid blue;
        margin: 10px;
       display: none;
      }
	</style>
    <script>
		$(function() {
        	$("#btn1").on("click", function() {
            	$("#divBox1").slideToggle();
			});
            $("#btn2").on("click", function() {
            	$("#divBox2").slideToggle(500);
			});
            $("#btn3").on("click", function() {
                $("#divBox3").slideToggle("fast");
			});
      	});
    </script>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>.slideToggle() 메소드</h1>
  <div>
    <button id="btn1">첫번째 슬라이드 토글</button>
    <div id="divBox1" class="wrap">안녕하세요.</div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <button id="btn2">두번째 슬라이드 토글</button>
    <div id="divBox2" class="wrap">devkuma입니다.</div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <button id="btn3">세번째 슬라이드 토글</button>
    <div id="divBox3" class="wrap">반갑습니다.</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>